#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:536
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will restore the application launcher as it was as default and remove "
"all your custom settings. A message box will ask you if you really want to "
"do that."
msgstr ""
"Ceci réinitialisera le lanceur d'application vers sa configuration par "
"défaut, et enlèvera tous vos réglages personnalisés. Un message vous "
"demandera de confirmer."

